    Plot chlorophyll and secchi data together with matrix outcomes

    show_plotlypep.Rd

    Plot chlorophyll and secchi data together with matrix outcomes

    Usage

    show_plotlypep(
  dat,
  bay_segment = c("Western", "Central", "Eastern"),
  yrrng = NULL
)

    Arguments

    dat

    data.frame formatted from read_pepwq

    bay_segment

    chr string for the bay segment, one of "Western", "Central", or "Eastern"

    yrrng

    numeric for year range to plot

    Value

    An interactive plotly object

    Examples

    show_plotlypep(rawdat)
